---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
import { business } from '../../data/business';
---
<Layout
  title="Stump Grinding Services | Mark's Stump Removal | Greenville, SC"
  description="Stump grinding, root removal, land clearing, and emergency stump services in Greenville, SC. Free estimates — call or text (864) 214-5623."
>
  <section class="bg-forest text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Our Stump Grinding Services</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-200">Professional equipment. Clean results. Fair prices.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white" id="stump-grinding">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl">🪵</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-forest">Stump Grinding</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-4">Our primary service — and what we do best. Using professional-grade stump grinders, we reduce tree stumps to wood chips 6–12 inches below the soil surface.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Any size stump — from small ornamental trees to massive hardwoods</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Grinding depth 6–12 inches below grade (deeper available on request)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Minimal disruption to surrounding lawn and landscaping</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Wood chips can be left as mulch or hauled away</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Most residential stumps completed in 30–60 minutes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16" id="root-removal">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl">🌿</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-forest">Root Removal</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-4">Surface roots and root balls can be tripping hazards, damage foundations, and make mowing a nightmare. We remove them cleanly.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Surface root grinding and removal</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Full root ball extraction for construction sites</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Invasive root system management</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Prevents regrowth and sucker shoots</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16" id="land-clearing">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl">🏗️</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-forest">Land Clearing</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-4">Building a new home? Adding a pool? Clearing a lot? We handle multi-stump jobs and brush removal to get your property ready.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Multi-stump lots and new construction prep</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Brush and undergrowth removal</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Volume discounts for large jobs</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Commercial and residential properties</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div id="emergency">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl">⚡</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-forest">Emergency Service</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-4">Storm damage can leave dangerous stumps and debris. We offer priority scheduling for urgent situations.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Priority scheduling for storm damage</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Hazardous stump removal</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Quick response times</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green font-bold">✓</span> Available for HOAs and property managers</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-forest mb-10">How It Works</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-earth text-forest rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">1</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-forest mb-2">Text Us a Photo</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Snap a photo of the stump from 10–15 feet away and text it to {business.phone}.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-earth text-forest rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">2</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-forest mb-2">Get Your Free Quote</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We'll review the photo and reply with a fair, no-obligation estimate — usually within hours.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-earth text-forest rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">3</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-forest mb-2">We Grind It Out</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We show up on schedule, grind the stump below grade, clean up, and leave your yard spotless.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA />
</Layout>
